## API clients
Accelerate your app development with BigCommerce API clients. The API clients are available in different programming languages such as Python, Php, Ruby, and JavaScript. See [Tools & Resources](https://developer.bigcommerce.com/tools-resources) for a list of our API clients.

## App starters
There are apps that every BigCommerce Enterprise customer should have to enhance their customer experience and sell more online. See [The BigCommerce Enterprise App Starter Kit](https://www.groovecommerce.com/ecommerce-blog/bigcommerce-enterprise-app-starter-kit/) for a list of the must-have apps for all store owners. 

## BigDesign
BigCommerce developed a collection of reusable React components, design guidelines, and UI patterns. This collection, known collectively as [BigDesign](https://developer.bigcommerce.com/api-docs/apps/guide/ui), allows you to rapidly develop an app's front-end that is consistent with BigCommerce's UI.

## SDK (Checkout SDK)
The Checkout SDK is a JavaScript library intended for partners, developers, and brands who want to build a custom checkout front-end experience. See [Checkout SDK](https://developer.bigcommerce.com/stencil-docs/customizing-checkout/checkout-sdk) for more information.
